OL,3,CLast few weeks have been 'like a bad
OL,4,Cdream': Ricky Hatton's brother
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports sports
OL,7,Fcorrespondent Mike Hall spoke
OL,8,Fexclusively to Matthew Hatton about
OL,9,Fhis brother, and the impact of his
OL,10,Fdeath
OL,12,FThe brother of Ricky Hatton has
OL,13,Fdescribed the weeks since the boxer's
OL,14,Fdeath as being "like a bad dream".
OL,16,FThe 46-year-old former World Champion
OL,17,Fwas found dead at his at home in Hyde,
OL,18,FGreater Manchester on Sunday 14
OL,19,FSeptember.
