OL,3,CLast few weeks have been 'like a bad
OL,4,Cdream': Ricky Hatton's brother
OL,6,FIn his first TV interview since his
OL,7,Fdeath, Ricky's younger brother,
OL,8,FMatthew Hatton, told ITV Granada
OL,9,FReports his death has still not fully
OL,10,Fhit him.
OL,12,F"I think when it first happened I was
OL,13,Fabsolutely, totally shocked and I'll
OL,14,Fbe honest for the first few weeks... I
OL,15,Fjust couldn't answer my phone. I
OL,16,Fcouldn't speak to people," Matthew
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,19,F"It felt almost like a bad dream. Has
OL,20,Fit hit me yet fully? Probably not."
