OL,3,CLast few weeks have been 'like a bad
OL,4,Cdream': Ricky Hatton's brother
OL,6,FThe two brothers spent their childhood
OL,7,Ftraining together, and went on to
OL,8,Ffight on the same cards for much
OL,9,Fprofessional careers.
OL,11,FMatthew said: "We were inseparable, we
OL,12,Fwere best friends. When I think back
OL,13,Fto the Vegas days, we needed each
OL,14,Fother.
OL,16,F"Boxing is a tough lonely game but we
OL,17,Fdid it together. The best time of my
OL,18,Flife and the best time of his life, I
OL,19,Ffeel fortunate we did them together. "
