OL,3,CLast few weeks have been 'like a bad
OL,4,Cdream': Ricky Hatton's brother
OL,6,FThe former welterweight boxer said his
OL,7,Fbrother's death came as a "total
OL,8,Fshock" to him and Ricky's entire
OL,9,Ffamily.
OL,11,FHe said: "Genuinely this year it's the
OL,12,Fbest he's even been by a long long way.
OL,14,F"He's had his problems since he
OL,15,Fstopped boxing, that's been well
OL,16,Fdocumented, but this is undoubtedly
OL,17,Fthe best we've ever seen him. So it
OL,18,Freally was a shock."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
