OL,3,CLast few weeks have been 'like a bad
OL,4,Cdream': Ricky Hatton's brother
OL,6,FOn Thursday 16 October, a coroner's
OL,7,Fcourt heard that Ricky was discovered
OL,8,F"unresponsive" by his manager, Paul
OL,9,FSpeak, and it is believed he had taken
OL,10,Fhis own life.
OL,12,FMatthew said he was aware of Ricky's
OL,13,Fstruggles with his mental health, and
OL,14,Falways worried about his brother.
OL,16,FHe said: "A lot of the time he spoke
OL,17,Fabout things that happened years ago,
OL,18,Fand didn't really seem to have a
OL,19,Fvision for the future and that always
OL,20,Fworried me...
