OL,3,CLast few weeks have been 'like a bad
OL,4,Cdream': Ricky Hatton's brother
OL,6,F"He was always so busy, so he didn't
OL,7,F(reach out) but I know he was speaking
OL,8,Fto professionals."
OL,10,FHatton had been candid about his
OL,11,Fmental health struggles with drink,
OL,12,Fdrugs and past suicide attempts after
OL,13,Fhe retired from the ring for a second
OL,14,Ftime following a misguided comeback in
OL,15,F2012.
OL,17,FHis death sparked a debate over
OL,18,Fwhether enough is being done to help
OL,19,Fsporting stars after retirement.
