OL,3,CLast few weeks have been 'like a bad
OL,4,Cdream': Ricky Hatton's brother
OL,6,FMatthew said: "Ricky loved being
OL,7,Faround people, he loved being in the
OL,8,Flimelight. He lived his life the way
OL,9,Fhe lived it. He didn't get ill, he
OL,10,Fdidn't fade into the background or
OL,11,Fgrow old where we all get a little bit
OL,12,Fless relevant.
OL,14,F"He would have absolutely hated that."
OL,16,FRicky Hatton received a huge send off
OL,17,Ffrom his home town, with thousands
OL,18,Flining the streets as his funeral
OL,19,Fcortege made it's way through Hyde,
OL,20,FDenton, and Manchester.
