OL,3,CLast few weeks have been 'like a bad
OL,4,Cdream': Ricky Hatton's brother
OL,6,FHe said: "I thought it was amazing. I
OL,7,Fexpected Hattersley where we grew up
OL,8,Fto be busy, and people did come out in
OL,9,Ftheir droves, but we went through
OL,10,Fdifferent places and it was pretty
OL,11,Fmuch all the way to the cathedral
OL,12,Fthere was people on the streets.
OL,14,F"You just could see the pain on their
OL,15,Ffaces and how much he meant to them.
OL,16,FFor the family it was such a great
OL,17,Fturnout and I can't thank people
OL,18,Fenough."
