OL,3,CLast few weeks have been 'like a bad
OL,4,Cdream': Ricky Hatton's brother
OL,6,FThe family has now set up the Ricky
OL,7,FHatton Foundation to help others who
OL,8,Fmay be suffering from mental health
OL,9,Fissues.
OL,11,FTalking about the foundation, Hatton's
OL,12,Fson Campbell said: "It's still very
OL,13,Fearly days with everything but a big
OL,14,Fpart of it is going to be around sport
OL,15,Fand educating people."
