OL,3,CLast few weeks have been 'like a bad
OL,4,Cdream': Ricky Hatton's brother
OL,6,F"The foundation is something we've
OL,7,Fbeen looking to do for a while and
OL,8,Fwe've never had the right time. Now is
OL,9,Fas good as time as we can get to carry
OL,10,Fhis legacy on and start tackling
OL,11,Fmental health," he added.
OL,13,F"The motto is 'no one should fight
OL,14,Falone' and it's going to be looking at
OL,15,Fhelping sportsmen, men, anyone really
OL,16,Fwho's struggling with mental health.
OL,18,F"Educating, raising awareness, and
OL,19,Factively tackling it through money
OL,20,Fraised so people don't have to
OL,21,Fstruggle alone."
