OL,3,CLast few weeks have been 'like a bad
OL,4,Cdream': Ricky Hatton's brother
OL,6,FThree weeks on from the death of his
OL,7,Folder brother, Matthew says it is his
OL,8,Ffond memories of Ricky that have
OL,9,Fhelped him to keep going.
OL,11,FHe said: "I'm at the stage now where
OL,12,FI'm starting to smile about it. I feel
OL,13,Fvery fortunate that I have all of
OL,14,Fthose great memories to make me feel
OL,15,Fbetter."
